Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,将力量结合起来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,漲る勇気
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,昂扬之勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,溢れる希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,满溢之希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光り輝く絆とともに！
